\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.767963131741216*^9, 3.7679631524919357`*^9}, {
  3.7679631982353563`*^9, 3.7679631982353563`*^9}, {3.768065882635975*^9, 
  3.7680659145467463`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e20d2919-7d61-4956-96f9-\
3f920abc1f00"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Should probably calculate / include the g --> gg splitting probability and \
include it at the same order, since we\[CloseCurlyQuote]re not just \
generating a new charge distribution, but also redistributing energy.  So \
there should also be a valid ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"O", "(", 
    SubscriptBox["\[Alpha]", "s"], ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "717a8e74-4fa3-45b9-8f28-b722e353cd0c"],
 " process that redistributes the energy but creates no charge"
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.767963131741216*^9, 3.7679631524919357`*^9}, {
  3.7679632032767973`*^9, 3.767963237008069*^9}, {3.7679632676201043`*^9, 
